  "title": "A shape-shifting UFO spotted hovering at a high altitude over Dourados-MS [2001]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/12/a-shape-shifting-ufo-spotted-hovering-at-a-high-altitude-over-dourados/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-mo",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>APRIL 15th, 2001</strong>. Time: 10:29 am. Duration: 13 minutes. A witness living in the city of Dourados, State of Mato Grosso do Sul, reported the sighting of an unidentified flying object hovering at an altitude of approximately 30,000ft and at a distance of 20km from the observer. The UFO shifted its shape, after being oval at first, and emitted a white light. The object hovered over the western sector of Dourados, and it was observed under good visibility and also recorded on video, but the video file was not made available.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo &#8216;Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)&#8217;. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.605. &#8220;</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre avistamento de ovni em Dourados, Mato Grosso do Sul&#8221;. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our &#8216;Info&#8217; page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [&#8220;Código de Referência&#8221;] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span></p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>APRIL 15th, 2001. Time: 10:29 am. Duration: 13 minutes. A witness living in the city of Dourados, State of Mato Grosso do Sul, reported the sighting of an unidentified flying object hovering at an altitude of approximately 30,000ft and at a distance of 20km from the observer. The UFO shifted its shape, after being oval [&hellip;]</p>\n",
